on-awards-1203428383/|title=\u2018For Sama\u2019 Wins Best Feature at International Documentary Association Awards|work=Variety|first1=Dave|last1=McNary|first2=Dano|last2=Nissen|date=8 December 2019|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|Pare Lorentz Award\n|Tamara Kotevska & Ljubomir Stefanov & Atanas Georgiev\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Director\n|Tamara Kotevska & Ljubomir Stefanov\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Feature\n|Tamara Kotevska & Ljubomir Stefanov & Atanas Georgiev\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[National Society of Film Critics| National Society of Film Critics Awards]]\n|[[National Society of Film Critics Award for Best Non-Fiction Film|Best Non-Fiction Film]]\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/national-society-film-critics-winners-2020-list-full-1266375|title='Parasite' Named Best Picture by National Society of Film Critics|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first1=Trilby|last1=Beresford|first2=Shareh|last2=Drury|date=4 January 2020|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2019 New York Film Critics Circle Awards|New York Film Critics Circle Awards]]\n|[[New York Film Critics Circle Award for Best Non-Fiction Film|Best Non-Fiction Film]]\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/new-york-film-critics-circle-awards-2019-winners-list-nyfcc-movies-1202800026/|title=New York Film Critics Circle Names \u2018The Irishman\u2019 Best Film; Safdie Brothers, Lupita Nyong\u2019o, Antonio Banderas Among Winners|date=4 December 2019|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Online Film Critics Society]]\n|[[Online Film Critics Society Award for Best Documentary Film|Best Documentary Film]]\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://filmpulse.net/the-online-film-critics-society-ofcs-announces-2019-award-winners/|title=The Online Film Critics Society (OFCS) Announces 2019 Award Winners|date=6 January 2020|website=Film Pulse|accessdate=20 January