 Film Critics Circle Awards]]\n|[[New York Film Critics Circle Award for Best Non-Fiction Film|Best Non-Fiction Film]]\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/new-york-film-critics-circle-awards-2019-winners-list-nyfcc-movies-1202800026/|title=New York Film Critics Circle Names \u2018The Irishman\u2019 Best Film; Safdie Brothers, Lupita Nyong\u2019o, Antonio Banderas Among Winners|date=4 December 2019|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Online Film Critics Society]]\n|[[Online Film Critics Society Award for Best Documentary Film|Best Documentary Film]]\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://filmpulse.net/the-online-film-critics-society-ofcs-announces-2019-award-winners/|title=The Online Film Critics Society (OFCS) Announces 2019 Award Winners|date=6 January 2020|website=Film Pulse|accessdate=20 January 2020|first=Adam|last=Patterson}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Producers Guild of America Awards 2019|Producers Guild of America Awards]]\n|[[Producers Guild of America Award for Best Documentary Motion Picture|Best Documentary Motion Picture]]\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/pga-awards-2019-documentary-nominations-producers-guild-1202789759/|title=PGA Awards Documentary Nominations: \u2018Apollo 11\u2019, \u2018American Factory\u2019, \u2018The Cave\u2019, \u2018Honeyland\u2019, Others Make The Cut|date=19 November 2019|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Erik|last=Pedersen|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[24th Satellite Awards|Satellite Awards]]\n|[[Satellite Award for Best Documentary Film|Best Documentary Film]]\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://awardswatch.com/international-press-academy-ipa-satellite-awards-ford-v-ferrari-races-to-the-top-with-5-wins/|title=International Press Academy (IPA) Satellite Awards: \u2018Ford v Ferrari\u2019 races to the top with 5 wins|website=Awards Watch|first=Erik|last=Anderson|date=19 December 2019|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Seattle Film Critics Society]]\n|Best Documentary\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nextbestpicture.com/2/post/2019/12/the-2019-seattle-film-critics-society-sfcs-nominations.html|title=The 2019 Seattle Film Critics Society (SFCS) Nominations|website=Next Best Picture|date=9 December 2019|accessdate=20 January 2020|first=Matt|last=Neglia}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[St. Louis Film Critics Association]]\n|Best Documentary Feature\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nextbestpicture.com/2/post/2019/12/the-2019-st-louis-film-critics-association-stlfca-nominations.html|title=The 2019 St. Louis Film Critics Association (StLFCA) Nominations|website=Next Best Picture|first=Matt|last=Neglia|date=8 December 2019|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[2019 Sundance Film Festival|Sundance Film Festival]]\n|World Cinema Grand Jury Prize: Documentary\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" |<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sundance.org/blogs/news/2019-sundance-film-festival-awards-announced|title=2019 Suundance Film Festival Awards Announced |website=Sundance.org|date=3 February 2019|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|World Cinema Documentary Special Jury Award for Impact for Change\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|World Cinema Documentary Special Jury Award for Cinematography\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[Vancouver Film Critics Circle]]\n|Best Documentary\n|''Honeyland''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/parasite-named-best-picture-by-vancouver-film-critics-circle-1262939|title='Parasite' Named Best Picture by Vancouver Film Critics Circle|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Etan|last=Vlessing|date=16 December 2019|accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Washington D.C. Area Film Critics Association]]\n|[[Washington D.C. Area Film Critics Association Award for Best Documentary|Best Documentary]]\